<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Payment Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for your payment. Here are the details of your transaction:</p>

    <div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee;">
      <h2>Session Details</h2>
      <p><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @session.title %></p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @session.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
      <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @session.start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> - <%= @session.end_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></p>
      <p><strong>Consultant:</strong> <%= @session.consultant.name %></p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee;">
      <h2>Payment Details</h2>
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@payment.amount) %></p>
      <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> <%= @payment.card_brand.titleize %> ending in <%= @payment.card_last4 %></p>
      <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> <%= @payment.stripe_payment_intent_id %></p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @payment.paid_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>Your Consulting Team</p>
  </body>
</html> 